result.reason: This is a Windows Server RDS session limit (not an mRemoteNG bug) — Windows 2012 R2+ enforces max concurrent RDP sessions via licensing/Group Policy, and mRemoteNG as an RDP client cannot bypass server-side session caps.
result.approach: Server-side limitation controlled by RDS CALs and Group Policy (MaxConnectionCount). No client-side fix possible in mRemoteNG.
